body:
“FOR HONOR!”

Here is @outcastcommander ‘s amazing oc Dagorlad Fett! I had so much fun with his mandalorian armor and mixing it with bits of jedi wardrobe! I added the cloak cause I thought it added some dramatics to the design😄thank you so much to outcastcommander for your patience💗if you have a Jedi oc you’d like me to draw please don’t be afraid to ask!! Just send a reference or description and we can work it out together!😄

May the force be with you, always!

blog.name: surferofrowdybliss
blog.title: Visual Play
blog.description:
Deborah Coulter

Scissors in hand, I make collages exploring the freedom and fun of visual play. I get lost in the joy of selecting, cutting, and rearranging images. The process begins as I discover the infinite possibilities life offers through the spaciousness of an open heart. Children, animals, and nature lead the way.

I invite you to join me in these adventures of scissors & glue blending with imagination in the exquisite present.

blog.name: druubii
blog.title: Drew B.
blog.description: My name is Drew, and this is where I post my illustrations!  Here you'll find drawings, stories, fan-art, and general fun.  Feel free to drop requests in the ask box, or message me so we can get to know one another!  I really like tea, plants, and cats (typical, I know), along with piano music and pretty things.  I have a strong sense of adventure, and I love intense and gripping stories - especially ones rife with character development.  My hope is to create emotionally gripping content that you enjoy.  Thank you for dropping by my tiny corner of the internet!
